      "content": "can u just tell me if it's common for appendicitis to feel like this? i feel like if it was actually a life or death thing i'd be incapacitated or something. i can still walk around, it's just uncomfortable. i feel like if i just take some extra ibuprofen and a heating pad i can manage it until i can see a gp tomorrow. it's probably just my cycle being weird this month, right? i really just want you to tell me it's nothing serious so i can stop stressing and sleep.",
